<h2>E-Mail</h2>
You can send e-mail to Bruce Schneier at <a
href="mailto:schneier@counterpane.com">schneier@counterpane.com</a> -- using his <a href="schneier.asc">PGP key</a>, if you like.  For website feedback and bug reports, please e-mail <a href="mailto:webfeedback@counterpane.com">webfeedback@counterpane.com</a>.

