<h2>Password Safe Support</h2>
Password Safe is now an open source project -- please see its <a href="http://sourceforge.net/projects/passwordsafe/">Sourceforge page</a> for feature requests and bug reports.  For support of 1.7.1 and earlier versions, please e-mail <a href="mailto:passwordsafe@counterpane.com">passwordsafe@counterpane.com</a>.


                  
